[[File:Hedera_helix1.JPG|thumb]]
'''常春藤'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|''Hedera helix''}}），又名'''洋常春藤'''、'''長春藤'''、'''土鼓藤'''、'''木蔦'''、'''百角蜈蚣'''，是[[常春藤屬|常春藤屬]]下的一種[[常綠植物|常綠]][[攀援植物|攀援植物]]，在很多地區常春藤實際都屬於[[入侵物種|入侵物種]]。

==命名==
常春藤的[[種加詞|種加詞]]''helix''來自[[古希臘語|古希臘語]]，意思是“扭”。<ref name=RHSLG>{{cite book|last=Harrison|first=Lorraine|title=RHS Latin for gardeners|year=2012|publisher=Mitchell Beazley|location=United Kingdom|isbn=978-1-84533-731-5|page=224}}</ref>

==描述==
其莖生氣根以攀緣他物，嫩葉以及花序被有星形鱗片，葉有柄，厚質，葡枝之葉稍做三角形，掌狀。

==分布==
常春藤自然分布于北至[[爱尔兰|爱尔兰]]東北部和[[斯堪的納維亞|斯堪的納維亞]]南部、南至[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]、東至[[烏克蘭|烏克蘭]]、[[土耳其|土耳其]]。在處於零下二攝氏度冬季等溫線以上的地區，一般會被其他植物取代。<ref name="Metcalfe">Metcalfe, D. J. (2005). [http://www.lclark.edu/org/kennedy/objects/Metcafle2005.pdf Biological Flora of the British Isles no. 268 Hedera helix L.] {{Wayback|url=http://www.lclark.edu/org/kennedy/objects/Metcafle2005.pdf |date=20090115210140 }} ''Journal of Ecology'' 93: 632–648.</ref><ref name="McAllister">McAllister, H. (1982). New work on ivies. ''Int. Dendrol. Soc. Yearbook'' 1981: 106-109.</ref><ref name="flora">[http://ip30.eti.uva.nl/BIS/flora.php?selected=beschrijving&menuentry=soorten&record=Hedera%20helix%20subsp.%20helix Flora of NW Europe]{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref name="Ackerfield">Ackerfield, J. & Wen, J. (2002). [http://www.mnhn.fr/publication/adanson/a02n2a6.pdf A morphometric analysis of Hedera L. (the ivy genus, Araliaceae) and its taxonomic implications.] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110808024417/http://www.mnhn.fr/publication/adanson/a02n2a6.pdf |date=2011-08-08 }} ''Adansonia'' sér. 3, 24 (2): 197-212.</ref><ref name="Europe">{{Cite web |url=http://rbg-web2.rbge.org.uk/cgi-bin/nph-readbtree.pl/feout?FAMILY_XREF=&GENUS_XREF=Hedera+&SPECIES_XREF=helix&TAXON_NAME_XREF=&RANK= |title=Flora Europaea: ''Hedera helix'' |access-date=2014-04-12 |archive-date=2007-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070930201728/http://rbg-web2.rbge.org.uk/cgi-bin/nph-readbtree.pl/feout?FAMILY_XREF=&GENUS_XREF=Hedera+&SPECIES_XREF=helix&TAXON_NAME_XREF=&RANK= |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>Stace, C. A. & Thompson, H. (1997). ''New Flora of the British Isles''. Cambridge University Press ISBN 978-0-521-58935-2</ref>

==與人類的關係==
叶有香气，形态优美，常作園藝观赏用。

其果實、種子和葉子均有毒，孩童誤食會引起腹痛、腹瀉等症狀，嚴重時會引發腸胃發炎、昏迷，甚至導致呼吸困難等。{{來源請求}}

===入侵植物===
人類將常春藤引入了許多地區，其中一些地區將其列為[[入侵物種|入侵物種]]。常春藤會迅速蔓延并纏繞其他植物造成後者死亡。它們創造了大片的“常春藤荒漠”（ivy deserts）。例如美國的許多州，特別是[[俄勒岡州|俄勒岡州]]全部禁止銷售與進口常春藤<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.oregonlive.com/business/index.ssf/2010/02/oregon_bans_sale_of_english_iv.html |title=Oregon bans sale of English ivy, butterfly bushes |access-date=2014-04-13 |archive-date=2018-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180528182723/http://www.oregonlive.com/business/index.ssf/2010/02/oregon_bans_sale_of_english_iv.html }}</ref><ref name="USDA">{{Cite web |url=http://plants.usda.gov/java/profile?symbol=HEHE |title=USDA Plants Profile: ''Hedera helix'' |access-date=2014-04-13 |archive-date=2007-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071210235800/http://plants.usda.gov/java/profile?symbol=HEHE |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://www.pesticide.org/pubs/alts/ivy/englishivy.html Controlling English Ivy] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081210184939/http://www.pesticide.org/pubs/alts/ivy/englishivy.html |date=2008-12-10 }}. Northwest Coalition for Alternatives to Pesticides.</ref>。[[太平洋西北地區|太平洋西北地區]]和[[美國南部|美國南部]]的政府也鼓勵消滅常春藤<ref name="nil">{{Cite web |url=http://www.portlandtribune.com/sustainable/story.php?story_id=117797294153983800 |title=Ivy chasers in a league of their own |access-date=2014-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110608040401/http://www.portlandtribune.com/sustainable/story.php?story_id=117797294153983800 |archive-date=2011-06-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="Arlington">[http://www.arlingtonva.us/Departments/ParksRecreation/scripts/parks/ivy.pdf Controlling English Ivy] {{Wayback|url=http://www.arlingtonva.us/Departments/ParksRecreation/scripts/parks/ivy.pdf |date=20140414072304 }} Arlington County, Virginia Department of Parks, Recreation and Community Resources.</ref>。

在[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]]南部，特别是東南部，常春藤被當做有害植物。在一些地區禁止販售常春藤<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dpi.vic.gov.au/dpi/vro/vrosite.nsf/pages/weeds_climbing_english_ivy|title=English Ivy (Hedera helix)|publisher=The State of Victoria|accessdate=17 September 2010|archive-date=2011-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110403035906/http://www.dpi.vic.gov.au/dpi/vro/vrosite.nsf/pages/weeds_climbing_english_ivy}}</ref>。與澳大利亞相鄰的[[新西蘭|新西蘭]]的環保局自1990年開始也將常春藤列為雜草（environmental weed）<ref>{{cite book|last=Howell|first=Clayson|title=Consolidated list of environmental weeds in New Zealand|publisher=Department of Conservation|location=Wellington|date=May 2008|series=DRDS292|url=http://www.doc.govt.nz/upload/documents/science-and-technical/drds292.pdf|isbn=978-0-478-14413-0|accessdate=2009-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090530024209/http://www.doc.govt.nz/upload/documents/science-and-technical/drds292.pdf|archive-date=2009-05-30|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

